<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 12:12:09 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>白宫：以色列呼吁转移加沙平民是“一项艰巨的任务”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/white-house-israels-call-to-move-gaza-civilians-is-a-tall-order/articleshow/104401299.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104401299.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 11:49:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/white-house-israels-call-to-move-gaza-civilians-is-a-tall-order/articleshow/104401299.cms</guid></item><item><title>阿富汗北部什叶派清真寺发生爆炸 恐造成人员伤亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/casualties-feared-in-blast-at-shiite-mosque-in-northern-afghanistan/articleshow/104400132.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104400132.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;一名政府官员称，周五阿富汗北部一座什叶派清真寺发生爆炸，造成多人受伤。 “什叶派清真寺发生爆炸。当局正在将伤者和死者送往医院，”事件发生地巴格兰省的官员毛拉维·哈希米 (Mawlawi Hashimi) 告诉路透社。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 11:16:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/casualties-feared-in-blast-at-shiite-mosque-in-northern-afghanistan/articleshow/104400132.cms</guid></item><item><title>约旦驱散前往约旦河西岸边境的亲巴勒斯坦抗议者</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/jordan-disperses-pro-palestinian-protesters-heading-to-border-with-west-bank/articleshow/104399684.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104399684.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;目击者称，约旦防暴警察周五强行驱散了数百名试图到达与以色列占领的约旦河西岸边境地区的亲巴勒斯坦抗议者，数千人在全国各地举行反以色列示威活动。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 11:04:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/jordan-disperses-pro-palestinian-protesters-heading-to-border-with-west-bank/articleshow/104399684.cms</guid></item><item><title>拉脱维亚称俄罗斯试图破坏与乌克兰护照裁决的边境</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/latvia-says-russia-trying-to-disrupt-border-with-ukraine-passport-ruling/articleshow/104399408.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104399408.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;拉脱维亚表示，下周将关闭与俄罗斯的一个过境点，此前该国指责莫斯科试图通过让乌克兰护照持有者通过这个小型农村检查站来制造混乱。拉脱维亚外交部表示，俄罗斯周四发布命令，称从下周开始，持有乌克兰护照的人只能通过莫斯科谢列梅捷沃机场或拉脱维亚文图利过境点进入俄罗斯领土。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 10:52:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/latvia-says-russia-trying-to-disrupt-border-with-ukraine-passport-ruling/articleshow/104399408.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列地面进攻迫在眉睫，哈马斯要求加沙居民呆在家里</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hamas-tells-gaza-residents-to-stay-home-as-israel-ground-offensive-looms/articleshow/104396554.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104396554.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;清真寺敦促加沙地带的居民留在家中，因为以色列军方已通知超过 100 万人向南迁移，以防遭到地面入侵。以色列军方与哈马斯之间的冲突已经达到关键点，以色列遭受了自1973年战争以来最血腥的袭击。以色列的猛烈空袭引发了人们对大规模入侵以消灭哈马斯的猜测，这让人想起 1948 年的浩劫。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 09:29:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hamas-tells-gaza-residents-to-stay-home-as-israel-ground-offensive-looms/articleshow/104396554.cms</guid></item><item><title>阿联酋向阿富汗地震灾民提供紧急人道主义援助</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/uae-dispatches-urgent-humanitarian-aid-to-people-affected-by-earthquake-in-afghanistan/articleshow/104398974.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104398974.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;阿拉伯联合酋长国立即向阿富汗受地震影响的赫拉特省提供救援援助，包括食品、医疗用品和实物援助，作为其在危机时期援助国家的持续承诺的一部分。该援助是为了执行阿联酋总统谢赫·穆罕默德·本·扎耶德·阿勒纳哈扬的指示。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 10:40:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/uae-dispatches-urgent-humanitarian-aid-to-people-affected-by-earthquake-in-afghanistan/articleshow/104398974.cms</guid></item><item><title>日本法院：要求手术改变文件性别违宪</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/unconstitutional-to-require-surgery-for-change-of-gender-on-documents-japan-court/articleshow/104398979.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104398979.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;日本中部一家法院周四裁定，要求跨性别者接受手术切除其现有生殖器官以便获得新性别的文件是违宪的。静冈家庭法院的判决维持了跨性别原告的请求，即在不进行手术的情况下将性别从女性改为男性，这一决定被 LGBTQ+ 倡导者誉为具有里程碑意义的决定。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 10:40:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/unconstitutional-to-require-surgery-for-change-of-gender-on-documents-japan-court/articleshow/104398979.cms</guid></item><item><title>法国北部学校教师遭持刀袭击身亡：报告</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/teacher-killed-in-knife-attack-in-school-in-northern-france-report/articleshow/104398183.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104398183.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据 BFM 电视台报道，法国北部城市阿拉斯周五发生了一起悲惨事件，一名教师在持刀袭击中丧生，多人受伤。当地执法部门证实发生了持刀袭击事件，地区当局确认袭击者已被逮捕。虽然细节仍在浮出水面，但警方无法核实媒体报道，称袭击者曾说出“真主至大”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 10:18:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/teacher-killed-in-knife-attack-in-school-in-northern-france-report/articleshow/104398183.cms</guid></item><item><title>伦敦犹太学校因安全担忧而关闭</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/jewish-schools-in-london-shut-down-amid-security-fears/articleshow/104397394.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104397394.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由于以色列冲突中的安全问题，伦敦的几所犹太学校决定周五继续关闭。关闭之前，英国首相里希·苏纳克宣布提供额外资金，以加强对该国犹太社区免受反犹太主义袭击的保护。学校担心该地区会发生反以色列抗议活动。虽然社区安全信托基金建议犹太学校应保持开放，但学校已经认真对待了这一决定。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 09:53:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/jewish-schools-in-london-shut-down-amid-security-fears/articleshow/104397394.cms</guid></item><item><title>普京：尽管西方制裁，俄罗斯仍扩大与独联体的经济联系</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/putin-russia-expanding-economic-ties-with-cis-despite-western-sanctions/articleshow/104396255.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104396255.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯总统普京在访问吉尔吉斯斯坦期间表示，尽管西方国家对莫斯科实施制裁，俄罗斯仍在加强与前苏联国家的经济关系。这是自国际刑事法院三月份对他发出逮捕令以来他首次出国旅行。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 09:19:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/putin-russia-expanding-economic-ties-with-cis-despite-western-sanctions/articleshow/104396255.cms</guid></item><item><title>随着关系稳定，澳大利亚将派遣高级官员参加中国防务论坛</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/australia-to-send-senior-official-to-china-defence-forum-as-ties-stabilise/articleshow/104396958.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104396958.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;澳大利亚将于10月派一名高级国防官员出席中国香山论坛，这是四年来的首次。该论坛被认为是中国对新加坡香格里拉对话的回应，将在北京接待外国国防官员。此举标志着北京和堪培拉之间在外交争端后紧张局势的缓和。预计美国代表也将出席。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 09:39:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/australia-to-send-senior-official-to-china-defence-forum-as-ties-stabilise/articleshow/104396958.cms</guid></item><item><title>拜登选择 16 个州的 7 个氢中心，获得 70 亿美元的美国拨款</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/biden-selects-7-hydrogen-hubs-across-16-states-for-7-billion-in-us-grants/articleshow/104395966.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104395966.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;乔·拜登总统将宣布用于发展区域氢中心的 70 亿美元联邦拨款的获得者。该计划旨在快速启动清洁氢气的生产和工业用户所需的基础设施。选定的中心将为 16 个州提供服务，并支持清洁氢气的生产、储存、运输和最终使用。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 09:11:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/biden-selects-7-hydrogen-hubs-across-16-states-for-7-billion-in-us-grants/articleshow/104395966.cms</guid></item><item><title>随着债务谈判取得进展，斯里兰卡总统将访华：消息来源</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/sri-lanka-president-to-visit-china-as-debt-talks-progress-source/articleshow/104393506.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104393506.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;斯里兰卡总统拉尼尔·维克勒马辛哈将于下周访问中国，与该国最大的银行讨论债务重组谈判。兼任财政部长的维克勒马辛哈一直在领导斯里兰卡努力管理其沉重的债务并从国际货币基金组织的计划中获得资金。他将出席在北京举行的“一带一路”论坛，并预计会见中国国家主席习近平。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 07:42:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/sri-lanka-president-to-visit-china-as-debt-talks-progress-source/articleshow/104393506.cms</guid></item><item><title>美洲“火环”日食：多云天气会破坏景色吗？</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/ring-of-fire-solar-eclipse-across-americas-will-cloudy-weather-ruin-the-view/articleshow/104392930.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104392930.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;周六，美洲数百万人将目睹罕见的“火环”日食。当月亮位于地球和太阳之间时，日食就会发生，在暗月周围形成明亮的阳光环。这种现象将沿着从俄勒冈州到巴西的狭窄路径可见，而西半球的其他地区将经历日偏食。多云天气可能会影响某些地区的能见度，预计俄勒冈州和加利福尼亚州北部的情况最糟糕。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 07:38:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/ring-of-fire-solar-eclipse-across-americas-will-cloudy-weather-ruin-the-view/articleshow/104392930.cms</guid></item><item><title>印尼总统否认政治王朝的言论</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/indonesian-president-brushes-off-talk-of-political-dynasty/articleshow/104393347.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104393347.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;印度尼西亚总统佐科·维多多（Joko Widodo）在任期即将结束时，对建立政治王朝的批评不予理睬。他表示，领导人的选择应该留给人民。然而，他任命亲属担任政治职务的做法引起了人们的担忧。佐科维的小儿子最近被任命为青年党领袖，他的女婿是棉兰市长，他的长子是梭罗市市长，也是潜在的副总统候选人。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 07:35:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/indonesian-president-brushes-off-talk-of-political-dynasty/articleshow/104393347.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国：老将有望接替失踪的国防部长</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/combat-veteran-is-top-contender-to-replace-chinas-missing-defence-minister/articleshow/104392229.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104392229.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;负责作战行动和规划的中国军事机构负责人刘振里将军很可能接替已经缺席公众视野六周多的国防部长李尚福。刘的任命可能会在地区紧张局势中改善与美国的军事接触。他并未受到西方制裁，据称接近军方和中国政界的消息人士可能会接替他。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 06:53:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/combat-veteran-is-top-contender-to-replace-chinas-missing-defence-minister/articleshow/104392229.cms</guid></item><item><title>匈牙利总理欧尔班：禁止支持“恐怖组织”的集会</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/hungary-to-ban-rallies-supporting-terrorist-organisations-pm-orban/articleshow/104392022.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104392022.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;匈牙利总理欧尔班维克托表示，该国不会允许任何支持“恐怖组织”的集会。他强调，所有匈牙利公民都应该感到安全，无论其信仰或出身如何。以色列领导人本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的盟友欧尔班表示，以色列有权自卫，但强调不要将冲突蔓延到其他国家并破坏该地区的稳定。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 06:45:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/hungary-to-ban-rallies-supporting-terrorist-organisations-pm-orban/articleshow/104392022.cms</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚警方在亲巴勒斯坦抗议前权衡特殊权力</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/australian-police-weigh-special-powers-ahead-of-pro-palestinian-protest/articleshow/104390066.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104390066.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;澳大利亚警方正在考虑二十年来首次对悉尼亲巴勒斯坦集会的参加者使用特别拦截搜查权。警方担心哈马斯入侵以色列后可能发生暴力事件。这项特殊权力最后一次使用是在 2005 年种族骚乱期间，允许警察无故搜查并索要身份。视频显示人们高喊反犹太口号后，这次集会引发了争议。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 05:37:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/australian-police-weigh-special-powers-ahead-of-pro-palestinian-protest/articleshow/104390066.cms</guid></item><item><title>拜登再次谈论宾夕法尼亚州的绿色能源和就业机会。他的消息会突破吗？</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/biden-is-talking-about-green-energy-and-jobs-in-pennsylvania-again-will-his-message-break-through/articleshow/104389135.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104389135.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 05:09:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/biden-is-talking-about-green-energy-and-jobs-in-pennsylvania-again-will-his-message-break-through/articleshow/104389135.cms</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾首都发生里氏5.2级地震：美国地质勘探局</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/magnitude-5-2-earthquake-shakes-philippine-capital-usgs/articleshow/104387728.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104387728.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;菲律宾发生里氏 5.2 级地震，马尼拉的建筑物发生震动，但没有造成人员伤亡或损坏的报告。地震发生在马尼拉以南，持续时间不到10秒。作为预防措施，学生和办公室工作人员撤离了他们的建筑物。由于菲律宾位于太平洋“火环”沿线，该地区以地震和火山活动而闻名，因此地震在菲律宾很常见。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 03:58:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/magnitude-5-2-earthquake-shakes-philippine-capital-usgs/articleshow/104387728.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>